{"tid":655490,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pay新增平台　iOS、PC也能用","createTime":"2018-05-06T14:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T01:06:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bbff90064ecfcaa2e5dbb333460f43c40788e3a8","tid":655490,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5aec246d374b722ecd453bbe_201805041714.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5aec246d374b722ecd453bbe_201805041714.png&h=9b21d16f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲Google 宣布 Google Pay 已可於 iOS 、 Linux 或 Windows PC 等平台使用。（圖／翻攝 Google Blog）</span></div><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 稍早宣布，旗下電子支付工具 Google Pay 5月4日起可以在更多平台上使用，包括 iOS 、 Linux 以及 Windows PC 等。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Pay 可使用於網路、實體店面、 Google 服務消費以及個人轉帳，使用者只要將個人 Google 帳號綁定信用卡等金融卡資訊，透過簡單認證方式即可完成線上交易，如此便無需在網頁上反覆填寫信用卡資訊，又能確保交易安全。目前已可用於 Chrome 、 Firefox ，以及 Safari 等瀏覽器。<br />\n<br />\n這樣方便快捷的行動支付服務已推向 20 多國，並可使用於全球數百萬家網站及實體店面，包括 Walgreens 、 Whole Foods ， Airbnb 等。<br />\n<br />\n於 2018 年 2 月上路的 Google Pay ，與蘋果 Apple Pay 較勁意味濃厚。蘋果旗下同樣提供行動支付服務 Apple Pay ，惟 Apple Pay 目前僅限蘋果裝置用戶使用，如 macOS 平台環境下的 Safari 瀏覽器，或是需要 iPhone 及 iPad 的 Touch ID 或 Face ID 功能以進行身分認證。相比於 Google 僅需登入個人帳號的作法，雖較為安全，使用上限制卻更多。<br />\n<br />\n網頁形式的 Google Pay ，同樣也支援點數卡累積功能，消費者在使用線上支付時，同時能享有信用卡提供的點數回饋。此項服務於美國地區先行上線，未來預計有更多店家加入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20180504/2748043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20180504%2F2748043&d=yrWxp8spTKOudE0FY6n35S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5a9f3ef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20180504/2748043</a>"},{"pid":"0a2afc0ad58447aa946336f0b6e13afa1386886e","tid":655490,"uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"如果八達通肯support Google Pay你哋話幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70c5da3daa23c0b750a3b0abc725ed6d37c1af3","tid":655490,"uid":92477,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"都係好事既 全球最大個兩間廠商都有自家pay<br />\n淨返低都係堆殘花敗柳<br />\n係時候擴展到更多唔同既平台<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/home_kv_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fhome_kv_2.jpg&h=1fc01ebf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"372b09b5ed74dadb8c809789e962c44cc733ef53","tid":655490,"uid":158977,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"ios<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 八達通<span style=\"color: red;\">app</span>仲未有得用nfc"},{"pid":"14b82e47eda0e43ac21544bf00fd010ce333e262","tid":655490,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"Google pay 係 ios唔係指用nfc"},{"pid":"3c0c0f750024426a83bc7e303c9e8894668220f5","tid":655490,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"In other words, when you're shopping on a website that supports Google Pay, you'll now see &quot;Buy with G Pay&quot; and &quot;G Pay&quot; buttons on your Android phone, iOS device, or whatever laptop or desktop you're using.<br />\n<br />\nCards you've added to the Google Pay app on your phone will automatically show up on sites that also support the platform, and when used, all your billing, payment, and shipping info will be filled out automatically."},{"pid":"842ef0db99dee29365d54d05c850988dcde9bc7f","tid":655490,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"同埋指入百佳卡個堆<br />\n我估"},{"pid":"95365fddcf7c98acf915e1af79cf5d83d89d737e","tid":655490,"uid":77104,"like":